  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Estimate the medical service of a system of navigation (IMACTIS-CT®)in terms of SAFETY,
      EFFICIENCY and PERFORMANCE, in comparison with the reference method during gestures of
      interventional radiology under scan in the thoraco-abdominal level.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
